content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4820.36 - Use of net proceeds

State Regulations

The entire net proceeds of all games of bingo must be
devoted to one or more of the lawful purposes as defined in the Bingo Licensing

Law and this Chapter. An organization failing to comply with this section will
be required to show cause before the commission why such organization's right
to conduct games of bingo should not be revoked. Notes
